      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "It's not clear to me why this is desirable. If two chains of equal work exist (correct me if I'm wrong, but the chance for this happening is pretty much zero), why not just wait until the next block to resolve the conflict? And if there are two chains of equal cumulative work, why choose one?",
